              <li class="list-group-item lgi-custom price-info">Instant IC Breakdown</li>
              <li class="list-group-item lgi-custom price-info">Business Type Analysis</li>
              <li class="list-group-item lgi-custom price-info"><script src="https://checkout.stripe.com/checkout.js" class="stripe-button"
